because the range of\ntemperature within the core is then smaller), and so high sensitivity is needed\nto detect them. Herschel, to be launched in 2007, will in principle provide the\nnecessary resolution and sensitivity at 170 to 250 micron.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Apr 2004 14:12:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
